{"tid":254213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報告指學生自殺涉多元成因包括精神病","createTime":"2017-05-23T04:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T08:21:13.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc476b5123041780d98a3f1c8edf969338919dd","tid":254213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"由去年9月開學至今，8個多月內已有20多名學生自殺身亡。防止學生自殺委員會報告指，學生自殺涉及多元成因，包括精神病。<br />\n<br />\n2016至17年度，到公立醫院求診的未成年抑鬱症患者有510人，較5年前增加近9成。<br />\n<br />\n有公立醫院精神科醫生表示，兒童及青少年精神科服務長期不足，非緊急個案輪候時間達1至3年"},{"pid":"275efc0c1eb59ad4ed164bde2f69831f1355b681","tid":254213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1331882-20170523.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1331882-20170523.htm&d=og%2B7FzeuXIWaWzWnPnBF5Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3716f8bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1331882-20170523.htm&h=ca361404\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1331882-20170523.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f335195f549d8c4df1413463bdf8e6f96f9ccdcd","tid":254213,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"又頼啦"},{"pid":"b9bba54e159de2ad69ab3cb8d24d254e739ccabd","tid":254213,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"其實 mi都有 環境因素。<br />\n所謂淨係屈mi = 自殺原因。 有點不公平"},{"pid":"61c9d7cd4a4110fa5fac97cf804b20aa3b8e6447","tid":254213,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0a7f6a4540d8706f58ae09db87c7329c2d1ff5","tid":254213,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"咁精神病係點形成先，包括精神病咁其他本身冇又點計"},{"pid":"6e167e0b9